OL,3,CDavey to take bus driving lesson in
OL,4,Ccall to scrap fare cap rise
OL,6,FSir Ed Davey will take a bus driving
OL,7,Flesson as he launches a Lib Dem
OL,8,Fcampaign calling for a Government U-
OL,9,Fturn on the rise of the bus fare cap.
OL,11,FThe #2 cap on single fares that
OL,12,Fapplies on most routes outside London
OL,13,Fwill be replaced by a new #3 cap until
OL,14,Fthe end of 2025, Chancellor Rachel
OL,15,FReeves announced in the Budget.
OL,17,FLiberal Democrats leader Sir Ed will
OL,18,Fmeet local bus company representatives
OL,19,Fat a bus depot in Oxfordshire on
OL,20,FFriday and hear their concerns about
OL,21,Fthe fare cap rise.
