OL,3,CDavey to take bus driving lesson in
OL,4,Ccall to scrap fare cap rise
OL,6,FHe will then take a bus driving lesson
OL,7,Faround the depot.
OL,9,FSir Ed said: "The fare cap increase is
OL,10,Flike a bus tax for people across the
OL,11,Fcountry, impacting bus users and
OL,12,Fcommuters already struggling to make
OL,13,Fends meet. MPs must be given a say on
OL,14,Fthis bus fare hike on behalf of their
OL,15,Fconstituents.
