OL,3,CDavey to take bus driving lesson in
OL,4,Ccall to scrap fare cap rise
OL,6,F"Our communities have already paid too
OL,7,Fhigh a price for years of Conservative
OL,8,Fneglect and incompetence. This bus
OL,9,Ffare hike will hit cherished local
OL,10,Fbusinesses and high streets, many of
OL,11,Fwhich are already struggling.
OL,13,F"The Government needs to change course
OL,14,Fand boost struggling local economies
OL,15,Fby investing in bus routes."
OL,17,FSingle bus fares in England have been
OL,18,Fcapped at #2 outside London, where
OL,19,Fthey are #1.75 per journey, for most
OL,20,Froutes since January 2023.
