OL,6,FOne in three bus users in England
OL,7,Foutside London say the fare increase
OL,8,Fmeans they will take the bus less
OL,9,Foften, a Savanta poll commissioned by
OL,10,Fthe Lib Dems found.
OL,12,FSavanta interviewed 1,437 adults in
OL,13,FEngland ` excluding London ` from
OL,14,FNovember 8 to 10.
