OL,3,CDavey to take bus driving lesson in
OL,4,Ccall to scrap fare cap rise
OL,6,FA Department for Transport
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The previous fare
OL,8,Fcap was due to expire at the end of
OL,9,F2024, with fares set to soar by as
OL,10,Fmuch as #13 on the most expensive
OL,11,Froutes, unless we intervened to keep
OL,12,Ffares down.
OL,14,F"Fares will only be allowed to
OL,15,Fincrease with inflation in the normal
OL,16,Fway, and the #3 bus fare cap will lead
OL,17,Fto savings of up to 80% on some
OL,18,Froutes, keeping bus tickets affordable
OL,19,Facross the country."
